# SE 3313B Mini Project - EcoSense xv6

## Overview
EcoSense is a sustainability-focused extension of the xv6 operating system.
It simulates environmental sensors and manages them efficiently using OS-level mechanisms.

## Features
- Sensor processes (temperature, air, energy)
- Adaptive sampling
- Shared data aggregation
- Alert system

## How to Run
make clean
make qemu

## How to Push into Github
git remote remove origin
git remote add origin https://github.com/NateNico/Mini-Project-ecosense-xv6-.git
git add .
git commit -m "...xv6 base for EcoSense project"
git branch -M main
git push -u origin main


